{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Welcome to Mega Corporation Mining Industry!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;Welcome to your new job as a <strong>Space Operator at\u00a0Mega Corporation Mining Industry</strong>. We expect nothing but excellence from you given your application. <strong>Do not disappoint us</strong>&quot;.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You wake up from your long sleep in the hyperchamber. But how did you actually pass the interview? Anyway, you must prove your skills now to make your parents proud.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/shoot-optimize.gif?t=1739875704\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Control your drone!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a world where resources are slim, you have to operate drones to win against other mega-companies in battles on various moons in order to harvest the resources from the moons.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy the calm yet exciting atmosphere of this retro 2D turn-based pixel game and capture the moons for the Mega Corporation Mining Industry.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/Whole_B_-_Gif.gif?t=1739875704\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Main features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>These are the currently available features. We aim to add more throughout Early Access.</i></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">19 unique missions across various moons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">6 endless minigames</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">9 different weapons of choice</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Try out the free demo and wishlist Space Operators now!</strong>\u00a0</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2736520/extras/ss_11469b9d4